- This program will create a pyramid of a given string, for example
Hello world to:
H
He
Hel
Hell
Hello
Hello 
Hello W
Hello Wo
Hello Wor
Hello Worl
Hello World
Hello Worl
Hello Wor
Hello Wo
Hello W
Hello 
Hello
Hell
Hel
He
H
- Examples of using prefixes and suffixes
'Hello ' - prefix
'World' - main text
' !' - suffix
Result:
Hello W !
Hello Wo !
Hello Wor !
Hello Worl !
Hello World !
Hello Worl !
Hello Wor !
Hello Wo !
Hello W !